{"tid":37224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老系列] 棄用紅綠燈 九旬翁遭小巴撞斃","createTime":"2016-12-13T08:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T12:10:07.000Z","uid":122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03544bec19ea8661d318a44b8378b9cf272c755f","tid":37224,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:32:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>棄用紅綠燈 九旬翁遭小巴撞斃</strong><br />\n<br />\n【13：30更新】男途人送院搶救不治。<br />\n<br />\n早上10時許，一輛紅頂小巴在筲箕灣東區走廊橋底駛出，右轉愛秩序灣道時，一名九旬老翁由車頭左至右行出過馬路。小巴收掣不及將他撞倒，老翁頭部受傷，昏迷送院搶救後不治。死者96歲姓蘇，52歲姓林小巴司機在場協助調查。現場附近有紅綠燈過路處，但疑有人沒使用，由行人路步出，斜線過馬路肇禍，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161213/large/1481611167_ef19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161213%2Flarge%2F1481611167_ef19.jpg&h=4f92f6a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主棄用紅綠燈過路處，由行人路步出行斜線過馬路，結果遭小巴撞斃；惟車禍後仍有市民(輪椅漢)同樣過馬路。(張培生攝)"},{"pid":"64bd54697da297ffe8c0a2f156844860d47f1c7e","tid":37224,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:35:27.000Z","msg":"96<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292210bd5b8da133676dba71a835cfb8503f9adf","tid":37224,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedb4b84e0465bfb96615768551da268b1597fbd","tid":37224,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:37:39.000Z","msg":"亂過馬路，害死人"},{"pid":"b5911aebd34e5f6eaae75437e548319e0f969eb3","tid":37224,"uid":13594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:38:15.000Z","msg":"輪椅麵咁過 痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd2b026895c22d97e2c3b3cfffa23659b49304c","tid":37224,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d360d577d20607f4172fd7a5df9a1ca8724ce0","tid":37224,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"害撚死個司機，祝個老野全家死晒無人葬佢"},{"pid":"802dd82865410546ee383a35d7bf806ebba8e970","tid":37224,"uid":15677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"我賽跑冠軍黎㗎"},{"pid":"369027819fd5fdf5ee1613fc4e03a235baddad27","tid":37224,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/b/bd/Fuxxgood.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20061207161138\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fb%2Fbd%2FFuxxgood.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20061207161138&h=1a1ac209&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09615dfb8c5f43af9ccba8f6af3b50ef86da28d0","tid":37224,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:03:15.000Z","msg":"遇上小巴佬 後生仔都冇命啦"},{"pid":"2a594fde0baa2755ffdff04d56c0144ec4cb182b","tid":37224,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遇上小巴佬 後生仔都冇命啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行返正式過路處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2baf202c78eb0bf9a67d69d38a76b3332ce27fc","tid":37224,"uid":35308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輪椅麵咁過 痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n架輪椅快過小巴好明顯"},{"pid":"28ef49a112b77a7b8fcc2e055205178ebeac0cb1","tid":37224,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/405_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fconten